load/2017/12/22/135829_9de3d99b3d28f6dfac55c4569e5f114f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F135829_9de3d99b3d28f6dfac55c4569e5f114f.jpg&h=888fdc57&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實呢 我唔會話無知可怕 但我洗唔洗連食左幾多年藥都要同你交代？我只係會當你on9囉 拎啲咁既文章出黎 算係點"},{"pid":"8564031276f8f2f55df1b485998e8fa4572efb6c","tid":506082,"uid":104793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T06:17:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/135829_9de3d99b3d28f6dfac55c4569e5f114f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F135829_9de3d99b3d28f6dfac55c4569e5f114f.jpg&h=888fdc57&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食緊venlafaxine 冇耐，冇咩感覺"},{"pid":"017a3b8dd7c276b9a956e8ee2fad14935e7aaee1","tid":506082,"uid":104793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T06:20:06.000Z","msg":"睇私家好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11c5fff717c1c1eb3fff036e927631067e52b23","tid":506082,"uid":121044,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T06:21:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/135829_9de3d99b3d28f6dfac55c4569e5f114f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F135829_9de3d99b3d28f6dfac55c4569e5f114f.jpg&h=888fdc57&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係你cap果啲唔一定岩哂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/142032_77d7b9684a8639381c7615e6e83e830e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F142032_77d7b9684a8639381c7615e6e83e830e.jpg&h=b8b5a63c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/142033_171463db0871e5c7f46387f96d17a5df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu